# 5. Domain-level aggregation

You also compute:

## Domain Health Score

* Average of all service scores
* Weighted by service criticality (optional)

### Output example

| Service   | Score | Status |
| --------- | ----- | ------ |
| Order     | 2.4   | 🔴     |
| Payment   | 3.8   | 🟢     |
| Inventory | 3.1   | 🟡     |

