# 6. Risk conversion layer (important)

Convert low scores into actionable risks:

| Condition         | Risk Flag                 |
| ----------------- | ------------------------- |
| Any dimension ≤ 1 | Critical risk             |
| Reliability ≤ 2   | High outage risk          |
| Architecture ≤ 2  | Distributed monolith risk |
| Observability ≤ 2 | Debugging risk            |
| Security ≤ 2      | Compliance risk           |

